    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S65B40 4.0L V8 with eight individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal front-mid engine layout ensures optimal weight distribution, while the M-specific suspension geometry and M Variable Differential Lock provide exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit traction. This example maintains its high-pressure VANOS system's integrity and features a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with short-throw precision. Recent service includes a comprehensive inspection of the subframe and rod bearings, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within factory tolerances. A driver-focused machine with the mechanical soul that modern turbocharged units lack, showing honest wear consistent with a well-",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
