    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between reliability and value. This car has been a dependable driver, kept in a climate-controlled garage and treated with consistent care. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips and superficial swirls consistent with regular road use. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the premium upholstery shows only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains taut over bumps. It has recently undergone a full fluid service and sits on tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle for someone who appreciates a car that has been respected rather than just driven. Non-smoker owned, no persistent odors, no leaks, and a clean title in hand.",
